{
  "texts": [
    "One of the identified reviews focused on the effects of burnout on patient outcomes and surgical professionalism, 21 while the other explored trends in burnout prevalence across Canada and America over time.",
    "Two investigators (AN and YYY) independently screened titles, abstracts and full texts for inclusion with disagreements resolved through discussion.",
    "The same manual method was used for all screening (Figure 1).",
    "Data from the included studies were extracted as follows: author name, title, year of publication, during COVID-19 pandemic, location and type of study, sample size, number of male and female participants, diagnostic tool and burnout definition used, outcome measures, intervention performed, duration of data collection and results.",
    "Data were extracted independently on a spreadsheet by two investigators (AN and YYY) and any disparities were resolved through discussion."
  ]
}